O Kunigo is a website created at feb/2010 that was build to crowd sourcing your projects. The main feature its let the users share tasks between projects (here called kunis). This sharing let you sync parts of your project with others projects with no pain. Using mongodb and sinatra the website could be used as base for your own website ideas.

This is the first version of the site. You can test this at: http://www.kunigo.com

Regards!!




