:::INSTALACAO DO SITE:
sudo gem install rake nokogiri hpricot builder cheat daemons json uuid fastthread rack
sudo gem install mongo_mapper --source http://gemcutter.org
sudo gem install mongo_ext
sudo gem install sinatra-r18n thin bcrypt-ruby erubis pony
sudo gem install sinatra 
